<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
</head>
<body class="admin-page">
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <h2><%= settings.siteName || 'OMTOGEL' %></h2>
    <a class="active" href="/pinktiger8008">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/pinktiger8008/settings">Pengaturan</a>
    <a href="/pinktiger8008/sliders">Slider Foto</a>
    <a href="/" target="_blank">Lihat Website</a>
    <form method="post" action="/pinktiger8008/logout"><button>Logout</button></form>
  </aside>
  <main class="admin-main">
    <h1>Dashboard Admin</h1>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat"><b><%= (settings.buttons || []).length %></b><span>Total Button</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b><%= (sliders || []).length %></b><span>Total Slider</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b>DATA_DIR</b><span>Aktif tersimpan di Railway Volume</span></div>
    </div>
    <section class="panel">
      <h2>Status Project</h2>
      <p>Website webview siap deploy. Semua logo, background, slider, nama tombol, dan link tombol bisa diatur dari admin.</p>
      <div class="quick-actions">
        <a href="/pinktiger8008/settings">Edit Pengaturan</a>
        <a href="/pinktiger8008/sliders">Edit Slider</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
